title: Diamond team is looking for MID & SUP
body:
Hello there, We are a three-side diamond team and we would love to make it five ;).
This season we want to achieve something in ranked flex.
Our aim is to reach (atleast) master.
We are looking for a midlaner and a support with the following qualifications:

-Diamond+ (euw)
-Large champion pool
-Able to communicate in english
-Willing to invest time and effort in this project.

If you are interested, you can add and contact Qbaser. I hope to meet you soon in the fields of justice!

http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=superpiratz

http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=Kiwifrukt

http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=Qbaser - https://play.eslgaming.com/player/1356152/
